{
  "name": "trove-cycle",
  "description": "Every 15 min: query agent verdict + Aave rewards. If movable: execute rebalance. If rewards >= threshold: claim them on user's behalf via Aave's setClaimer-authorized path. Log everything to 0G Storage and commit memoryHash to iNFT.",
  "tags": ["trove", "0g", "aave-v3", "base-mainnet"],
  "trigger": {
    "type": "cron",
    "schedule": "*/15 * * * *",
    "timezone": "UTC"
  },
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "tick",
      "type": "http",
      "config": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "${AGENT_BASE_URL}/api/agent/tick",
        "query": {
          "address": "${USER_ADDRESS}",
          "principalUsd": "${PRINCIPAL_USD}"
        },
        "timeout_ms": 8000
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "rewards_check",
      "type": "http",
      "config": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "${AGENT_BASE_URL}/api/agent/rewards",
        "query": {
          "address": "${USER_ADDRESS}"
        },
        "timeout_ms": 8000
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "branch_verdict",
      "type": "switch",
      "depends_on": ["tick"],
      "config": {
        "expression": "${tick.body.verdict}",
        "cases": {
          "move": "execute_rebalance",
          "harvest": "execute_harvest",
          "hold": "log_and_exit"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "branch_rewards",
      "type": "switch",
      "depends_on": ["rewards_check"],
      "config": {
        "expression": "${rewards_check.body.unclaimed.length > 0}",
        "cases": {
          "true": "execute_claim_rewards",
          "false": "skip_claim"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "execute_rebalance",
      "type": "tx",
      "depends_on": ["branch_verdict"],
      "config": {
        "chain_id": 8453,
        "to": "${tick.body.txPayload.to}",
        "data": "${tick.body.txPayload.data}",
        "value": "0",
        "gas_strategy": "network_average",
        "max_priority_fee_gwei": 0.01
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "execute_harvest",
      "type": "tx",
      "depends_on": ["branch_verdict"],
      "config": {
        "chain_id": 8453,
        "to": "${tick.body.txPayload.to}",
        "data": "${tick.body.txPayload.data}",
        "value": "0",
        "gas_strategy": "network_average"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "execute_claim_rewards",
      "type": "tx",
      "depends_on": ["branch_rewards"],
      "config": {
        "chain_id": 8453,
        "to": "${rewards_check.body.claimTx.delegated.to}",
        "data": "${rewards_check.body.claimTx.delegated.data}",
        "value": "0",
        "gas_strategy": "network_average",
        "_note": "Uses claimAllRewardsOnBehalf — requires user to have called setClaimer(user, KEEPERHUB_TURNKEY_WALLET) once. Rewards land directly in user's wallet."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "skip_claim",
      "type": "noop",
      "depends_on": ["branch_rewards"]
    },
    {
      "id": "log_and_exit",
      "type": "noop",
      "depends_on": ["branch_verdict"]
    },
    {
      "id": "upload_memory",
      "type": "http",
      "depends_on": [
        "execute_rebalance",
        "execute_harvest",
        "log_and_exit",
        "execute_claim_rewards",
        "skip_claim"
      ],
      "config": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "${AGENT_BASE_URL}/api/agent/log",
        "body": {
          "address": "${USER_ADDRESS}",
          "verdict": "${tick.body.verdict}",
          "reason": "${tick.body.reason}",
          "rebalance_tx": "${execute_rebalance.tx_hash}",
          "harvest_tx": "${execute_harvest.tx_hash}",
          "claim_tx": "${execute_claim_rewards.tx_hash}",
          "claimed_rewards": "${rewards_check.body.unclaimed}"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "commit_inft",
      "type": "tx",
      "depends_on": ["upload_memory"],
      "config": {
        "chain_id": 16602,
        "to": "${tick.body.iNftCommit.contract}",
        "function": "updateMemory(uint256,string)",
        "args": [
          "${tick.body.iNftCommit.tokenId}",
          "${upload_memory.body.memoryHash}"
        ],
        "gas_strategy": "fixed",
        "gas_limit": 80000
      }
    }
  ],
  "env_vars": {
    "AGENT_BASE_URL": "https://trove.web3wagmi.com",
    "USER_ADDRESS": "0x...",
    "PRINCIPAL_USD": "10000",
    "KEEPERHUB_TURNKEY_WALLET": "0x1A09587D1f8D7BFB88454Abd51EB0354A2fdeDDd"
  },
  "_notes": [
    "Two parallel checks per cycle: tick (rebalance/harvest decision) and rewards_check (claimable Aave incentives).",
    "rewards_check → branch_rewards → execute_claim_rewards uses Aave's claimAllRewardsOnBehalf — KeeperHub's Turnkey wallet must be pre-authorized by the user via Aave RewardsController.setClaimer(user, KEEPERHUB_TURNKEY_WALLET).",
    "Claimed rewards always land in the user's wallet, not KeeperHub's. The setClaimer permission only allows claiming, not redirecting.",
    "All branches converge on upload_memory → commit_inft so every cycle (even pure HOLD) updates the iNFT memoryHash.",
    "Fund the KeeperHub Turnkey wallet with Base ETH for gas before enabling tx nodes.",
    "execute_rebalance and execute_harvest still require a protocol-specific calldata adapter to be wired; execute_claim_rewards uses Aave's standard ABI directly and works today."
  ]
}
